The Glenn Beck Program

      The Glenn Beck Program - 3/7/14Friday, March 07, 2014 11:27 AM





Glenn is annoyed because with all that's happening in our country
    and all the issues the Obama administration is facing

         but nope, he's on yet another vacation.

  Also, Glenn tells you why he doesn't want you to take Donald Trump seriously as a candidate.

           Plus, the fake chef making rounds on the local TV circuit.
